#: ../../source/unit/neco.rst:7 3ed3f095ddda4713b1cd70bef7f04f21
msgid ""
"The Neco Unit is a unique RGB light board unit that features an adorable "
"cat ear shape. It is designed with precision and comprises 35 "
"WS2812C-2020 RGB lamp beads, providing vibrant and customizable lighting "
"effects."
msgstr ""
"Neco Unit 是一款独特的 RGB 灯板单元，采用可爱的猫耳造型。它经过精密设计，由 35 颗 WS2812C-2020 RGB "
"灯珠组成，可提供鲜艳且可自定义的灯光效果。"

